# ðŸŽ¯ Quick Reference - React Context Patterns & UI Design

## React Context Architecture

### 1. Auth Context Pattern
```typescript
// app/components/auth-context.tsx
interface AuthContextType {
  user: User | null;
  profile: UserProfile | null;
  loading: boolean;
  signIn: (email, password) => Promise<{ error }>;
  signOut: () => Promise<void>;
}

export function AuthProvider({ children }) {
  const [user, setUser] = useState<User | null>(null);
  
  useEffect(() => {
    supabase.auth.onAuthStateChange((event, session) => {
      setUser(session?.user ?? null);
    });
  }, []);

  return <AuthContext.Provider value={{...}}>{children}</AuthContext.Provider>;
}
```

### 2. Cart Context Pattern
```typescript
interface CartContextType {
  items: CartItem[];
  addItem: (item) => void;
  removeItem: (id) => void;
  clearCart: () => void;
  total: number;
}
```

### 3. Language/i18n Context Pattern
```typescript
interface LanguageContextType {
  language: 'en' | 'vi';
  setLanguage: (lang) => void;
  t: (key: string) => string; // Translation function
}
```

---

## Tailwind Design System

### Custom Color Palette
```javascript
// tailwind.config.js
colors: {
  'pearl': {
    50: '#fefefe',
    500: '#f0f0f0',
    900: '#9a9a9a',
  },
  'silk': {
    white: '#fefefe',
    lavender: '#f3f0ff',
    rose: '#fdf2f8',
  },
}
```

### Glass-Morphism Utilities
```css
.glass-card {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
}
```

### Custom Animations
```javascript
animation: {
  'fade-in': 'fade-in 3s ease-in-out forwards',
}
```

---

## UI Component Patterns

### Loading State Pattern
```typescript
function Component() {
  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(true);
  const [data, setData] = useState(null);

  if (loading) return <LoadingSpinner />;
  if (!data) return <EmptyState />;
  return <DataView data={data} />;
}
```

### Error Boundary Pattern
```typescript
class ErrorBoundary extends React.Component {
  componentDidCatch(error, errorInfo) {
    logErrorToService(error, errorInfo);
  }
  
  render() {
    if (this.state.hasError) {
      return <ErrorFallback />;
    }
    return this.props.children;
  }
}
```

---

## Key Takeaways

- **Context for Global State**: Auth, Cart, Language
- **Custom Tailwind Theme**: Consistent design language
- **Glass-Morphism**: Modern, elegant UI
- **Loading States**: Always show feedback
- **Error Handling**: Graceful degradation

